  "texts": [
    "Additionally, more than half (58%) have had positive past experiences with AI-enhanced education, reinforcing its potential benefits.",
    "Furthermore, a considerable majority (62 percent) believe that AI-enhanced education signifies the future of learning, emphasizing AI's evolving and influential role within the education domain.",
    "However, it's worth noting that there are concerns about potential negative impacts, with 56 percent expressing worries.",
    "Understanding and addressing these concerns is crucial for responsible AI integration in education.",
    "This data provides valuable input regarding the current usage of AI-enhanced educational tools, with 48 percent of respondents indicating their frequent use."
  ]
}